hobbies.title: Video games

hobbies.title: Walking
hobbies.bio: Combining resting my mind after learning, moving, something I can do on my own with minimal planning and that will also benefit me mentally and physically

hobbies.title: Cooking
hobbies.bio: I like simple hobbies I can improve on, that I can do when I want and that adds to my life. Getting better at cooking is great for one's health, wallet, and mind

hobbies.title: Painting

hobbies.title: Drawing

hobbies.title: Reading
hobbies.bio: A 2018 New Year's resolution that stuck, the simplicity of the medium yet complexity in content both relaxes and brings my brain on adventures.
